solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public List<String> fizzBuzz(int n) {--newline--        List<String> ret = new ArrayList<String>(n);--newline--        for(int i=1,fizz=0,buzz=0;i<=n ;i++){--newline--            fizz++;--newline--            buzz++;--newline--            if(fizz==3 && buzz==5){--newline--                ret.add("FizzBuzz");--newline--                fizz=0;--newline--                buzz=0;--newline--            }else if(fizz==3){--newline--                ret.add("Fizz");--newline--                fizz=0;--newline--            }else if(buzz==5){--newline--                ret.add("Buzz");--newline--                buzz=0;--newline--            }else{--newline--                ret.add(String.valueOf(i));--newline--            }--newline--        } --newline--        return ret;--newline--    }--newline--}--newline--
